# Pythagorean Theorem
  Right Triangle

            |\
            |  \
            |    \
            |      \
            |        \
  b         |          \   c
  opposite  |            \ hypotenuse  5*5
  3*3       |              \
            |                \
            |                  \
            |                    \
            |                      \
            |.                     α \
             -------------------------
                    a adjacent
                       4*4
  
a^2+b^2=c^2      4^2+3^2=5^2 = 16+9 = 25
√c^2=√a^2+b^2
c=√a^2+b^2


